<h1 id="your-demo-was-never-a-demo-of-your-product">Your demo was never a demo of your product</h1>

<p>It took me a while to realize that a â€˜demoâ€™ in the SaaS world is actually not supposed to be a â€˜demoâ€™. A demo here means that you and a prospect are discussing a potential solution(not the product) to their problems.</p>

