<h1 id="how-do-we-have-this-conversation">How do we have this conversation?</h1>

<p>Iâ€™m the guy my friends and family come to when they want to buy a new phone. Iâ€™m updated on the latest phones and the features they bring. I read tech blogs a lot.</p>

<p>I qualify for the â€˜What phone should I buy next?â€™ because I donâ€™t tell them the BEST phone. I suggest a phone thatâ€™s within their budget and can do most of what they want. If it canâ€™t do anything, I tell them that as well.</p>

