<h2 id="dont-just-be-a-product-expert-be-a-domain-expert">Donâ€™t just be a product expert, be a domain expert</h2>

<p>Product knowledge is overrated. Develop domain expertise and truly become a consultant. Read blogs, watch videos and most importantly â€” talk to people and learn from their experience.</p>

