<h2 id="avoid-your-language-talk-their-language">Avoid your language, talk their language</h2>

<p>You know your product like the back of your hand. Your prospects are looking at it for the first time. Thereâ€™s a BIG gap. A â€˜demoâ€™ is not the time to show off your product knowledge. My target before every first product conversation is to not use a single word from my product.</p>

